comments: Claxton (BKN) turns slightly as he firms up in his screening position and absorbs the contact made with Green (PHI).
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Green's (PHI) path and absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) rests his hand on Shamet's (BKN) left arm and marginal contact occurs during Shamet's drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Brown (BKN) moves forward into Korkmaz's (PHI) space and initiates body contact that affects Korkmaz's SQBR. The contact occurs before any potential dribbling violation.
Korkmaz (PHI) reflexively places his arms to Claxton's (BKN) upper half as the pick is set and quickly releases.
Embiid (PHI) jumps alongside Brown's (BKN) path and marginal body contact is initiated by Brown before Embiid cleanly blocks his shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) initiates contact with Simmons' (PHI) back and side after Simmons gains control of the rebound.
Simmons (PHI) moves alongside Shamet's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as Shamet drives toward the lane.
Simmons (PHI) extends forward and delivers contact to Shamet's (BKN) side, affecting Shamet's SQBR.
Claxton (BKN) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Claxton (BKN) is retreating away from Embiid (PHI) and marginal contact occurs with Embiid's side as he dribbles out of the post.

Replay review of the foul called on Johnson (BKN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Johnson is moving forward as he initiates contact with Embiid's (PHI) front and arm, affecting Embiid's SQBR.
After initially engaging with one another, Shamet (BKN) extends both hands against Simmons' (PHI) front and dislodges Simmons from his position.
Korkmaz (PHI) cleanly strips the ball away from Johnson (BKN) before any incidental contact occurs.
Johnson (BKN) brings his hand to Embiid's (PHI) front and marginal contact occurs as the double team comes. Shamet (BKN) then makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Embiid.
Johnson (BKN) makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) left arm causing him to lose control of the ball.
Green (PHI) legally goes into the backcourt to retrieve the ball after Embiid (PHI) fumbles it.
Johnson (BKN) delivers body contact to Green (PHI) that dislodges him from position after he retrieves the loose ball.
Brown (BKN) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Claxton (BKN) grasps and then quickly releases Embiid's (PHI) right leg during rebounding.
Shamet (BKN) continues moving forward after the hand-off and incidental body contact occurs with Green (PHI) along the perimeter.
Simmons (PHI) moves alongside Johnson's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Johnson's driving shot attempt.
